Title: prism_alerts: alert sorting was compromized
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1604407736
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0b1

Sorting alerts was buggy leading to random alerts being chosen to be the worst of all.
This fix now takes the real worst of all alerts, which might lead to less optimistic check results.
